00名澳門人早年因聽信當地特首崔世安宣揚大灣區發展，又誤信大灣區江門巿一個大型商住樓花項目，由政府支持十分穩陣，遂分別以18萬至過百萬元購買，直至去年中他們才驚覺樓盤入伙無期。過去多個月，他們自組的微信苦主群已升至2,500人，包括粵港澳人，他們多次到地盤請願，又寫信給崔世安，但事件毫無寸進，於是趁今年2月21日粵港澳三地官員在港舉行會議，苦主們計劃到場請願，並在群內留下姓名、電話及來自地區等，好讓召集人統籌。<br />\n<br />\n澳門人林小姐當日早上7時許，相約2名澳門苦主一起來港，「平時我用自動過關，暢通無阻，但當日按很多次手指模都唔得。」之後她被海關帶進一間房，問她：「你去香港做甚麼？去邊？幾時返？」又要求她簽下個人資料證明書，並寫上姓名、地址、電話、職業、父母姓名等。「我問佢究竟發生咩事，我犯了甚麼事，但佢哋只說電腦故障。」林小姐填過證明書，擾攘約15分鐘後才獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n林小姐直言事件黑暗，估計有網警滲入其苦主群內，收集情報，「澳門政府之前只會限制別人入境，但估不到連普通市民都被限制出境，我冇犯事，點解控制我嘅自由，日後會唔會好似內地咁上門騷擾。」<br />\n<br />\n損失過百萬元的黃小姐當日也遇上相同事件，首次維權的她慨嘆：「澳門人一向較沉默，連早年政府推出23條立法，大部份市民包括我都覺得事不關己，但現在我親身經歷過，一個受害者合法爭取權益，出境時都受阻撓，我覺得自己唔可以沉默下去。」<br />\n<br />\n她反問：「法律是要保護受害者，但點解當維權涉及領導利益時，我們就受阻撓？回歸20年已倒退到咁，我們嘅子孫會去到咩地步？係咪可以用一個莫須有罪名，就可將我哋入罪？」<br />\n<br />\n她說當初因粵港澳三地政府大力推廣，崔世安又兩次親自前往考察，她才投資大灣區項目，最終卻爛尾收場，「我寫信畀崔世安，但佢回信只答已知悉，未有回應我哋嘅訴求。將來被納入大灣區居民，我覺得非常危險，當遇問題，只有好似內地咁，被打壓，我寧願移民算了。」<br />\n<br />\n在澳門長大的Cici當日堅持不簽個人資料證明書，最終海關也無奈放她走，事後她更得知其中一名澳門搞手，在請願前一日到珠海，過關時遭扣查，要求他簽下證明書，承諾一周內不去香港。「好恐怖！讀書時聽過吾爾開希搞民運嘅遭遇，以為係歷史，點知發生喺自己身上，點解澳門話回歸50年不變，但20年唔夠已經倒退？」她不知道當局如何取得苦主來港維權的名單，但她聲言不會就此放棄，會繼續爭取自己權益。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:14:00.000Z","msg":"嘩，帶曬帽同口罩，好似病得好嚴重咁，講咁多不如去睇左醫生先啦"},{"pid":"1f9e282d9860e3705db042982376baf708c33035","tid":1112902,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e0004b24474a99ab7a58ef7a6a2a04def0d9c47","tid":1112902,"uid":182550,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"反大陸買樓都係信黨<br />\n想行大陸戈套<br />\n依家又話要人權<br />\n最搞笑戈班人仲用wechart  開group"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:17:42.000Z","msg":"反大陸？<br />\n反大陸買樓？<br />\n點解反對上大陸買樓就係信黨？"},{"pid":"84a3ce3b4607b72baa0bb586247cdeca2d41fb12","tid":1112902,"uid":25794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:18:36.000Z","msg":"唔係話好過香港好多既咩<br />\n嘈咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e420a5fe600947458a60fa6a9c1a8c76f350ec","tid":1112902,"uid":143033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75c5a420bcbb7639e05c96e29efd10eed7619ba1","tid":1112902,"uid":63671,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:27:54.000Z","msg":"其實如果有睇咩叫123事件嘅人就會明點解澳門點解紅到咁<br />\n佢地係比人由66年殖民到依家，同香港唔同<br />\n未計葡萄牙真係臭閪國家黎"},{"pid":"5c840bf272b729a2279035b07f70f80b923ca04b","tid":1112902,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5378dcb5cafaf752d1c22fd05878a065ec201dac","tid":1112902,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T21:38:27.000Z","msg":"你本葡萄牙護照呢？<br />\n係時候用啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"早出世先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b31ace39164cd92c2ca84289dc9509becb6fd4","tid":1112902,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:43:05.000Z","msg":"再一次提提各位，人地比人強姦起碼有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8391ba659fe29a47baa2de14ccc594d6da691c9","tid":1112902,"uid":224510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c840bf272b729a2279035b07f70f80b923ca04b","tid":1112902,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5378dcb5cafaf752d1c22fd05878a065ec201dac","tid":1112902,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T21:38:27.000Z","msg":"你本葡萄牙護照呢？<br />\n係時候用啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"早出世先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:48:02.000Z","msg":"但有世襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c02dd4993e58356c7530d2058f8cea586439a9c","tid":1112902,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c413b4766dea27429c9ab05067e35d04cf8cfac2","tid":1112902,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:52:56.000Z","msg":"澳門年年派錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登仔好眼紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499df68e6f3d6b8212e0add52dc6237b11a2bbd1","tid":1112902,"uid":54060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a54450ffcdb6cb4b22eb3d691c3c05dc35cd94b2","tid":1112902,"uid":58335,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"cc545a478d369aab6b1fb902cd03953d14cfe3c0","tid":1112902,"uid":128417,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T16:32:21.000Z","msg":"問: 不知道當局如何取得苦主來港維權的名單<br />\n答: 自組的<span style=\"color: red;\">微信</span>苦主群已升至2,500人<br />\n<br />\n用微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"蠢撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過澳門好似係好興用we柒<br />\n有tg，wts唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳豬真係澳豬<br />\n事不關己<br />\n好快到港豬架啦<br />\n<br />\n黎香港示威做乜鳩<br />\n上次又係有班大陸人嚟香港示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n澳豬同蚑那蝗嚟香港示威有撚用咩<br />\n港共政府都要睇蚑共頭<br />\n真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3e84456cae8c380bc37eba0f4687f529f92bd8","tid":1112902,"uid":245849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:53:15.000Z","msg":"難聽都要講句：點解訪問依幾個澳門人可以天真成咁，重要有人讀過下歷史，都唔明中共係咩嚟？<br />\n<br />\n政治講既唔單純係對錯是非或政客選舉，而係每一個人自身嘅保障同權益，我已經唔係講到自由公平果種權益，而係更基本人身安全及財產。<br />\n<br />\n中共係唔會&quot;俾&quot;個權大家，因為無事時佢地靠收割人民致富，大陸機會處處？你有冇關系網先？結果個關系網背後都係中共控制﹔有事時就收割人民保命，個權一直都係中共政府手上，佢可以係某省某市強拆、掃蕩人口等，點解唔可以對澳門香港咁做？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係問佢會唔會咁做，而係問佢點解可唔可以。<br />\n<br />\n佢可以咁做係唔係，國比家大嘛，政府比人民重要嘛，對於港澳兩地嘅人黎講，跟本就係我地上幾代人將把狗頭鍘放係佢地自己同後代頸上。<br />\n<br />\n唔好天真啦，想要自由公平，當然要反共，想要安全保家，都係要反共。你覺得中共國内出事係自找或唔好彩，得咁同大家講，中共只係唔殺雞取卵而已。<br />\n<br />\n中共治下冇人民，只有家禽。"},{"pid":"23bb353568069608a489b47e0d40939c23a85f79","tid":1112902,"uid":17932,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:04:25.000Z","msg":"港豬憑咩笑人<br />\n五十步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ac45c3617a4c24b4f89c6bc6958056b0d39d4e","tid":1112902,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c840bf272b729a2279035b07f70f80b923ca04b","tid":1112902,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5378dcb5cafaf752d1c22fd05878a065ec201dac","tid":1112902,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T21:38:27.000Z","msg":"你本葡萄牙護照呢？<br />\n係時候用啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"早出世先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:04:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗，老母有咪得，佢實早出世啦<br />\n又唔係BNO"},{"pid":"85d25892f78984a42ad0fee789971fa68ee630dd","tid":1112902,"uid":128328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T01:06:28.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，平時唔係話好撚多機遇架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec1452ef41f5783291dc6cb5c614ddc10410bd0","tid":1112902,"uid":128328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946915f46fb5011f4ed9d8486d6da7c2eeed490a","tid":1112902,"uid":179409,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"c60a9f42965aa9379f28946aebb574a3da60b9b5","tid":1112902,"uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"cc545a478d369aab6b1fb902cd03953d14cfe3c0","tid":1112902,"uid":128417,"like":58,"dislike":0,"score":58,"